menu "PIR Sensor Configuration"

    config PIR_SENSOR_ENABLED
        bool "Enable PIR motion sensor"
        default y
        help
            Start a task that monitors the PIR sensor output pin and logs
            motion events. The pin can be selected below.

    config PIR_SENSOR_GPIO
        int "PIR sensor OUT GPIO number"
        depends on PIR_SENSOR_ENABLED
        default 20
        range 0 54
        help
            GPIO connected to the PIR sensor OUT signal.
            On ESP32-P4-Function-EV-Board J1 header, GPIO20 is pin 13.

    config PIR_SENSOR_TASK_STACK_SIZE
        int "PIR sensor task stack size"
        depends on PIR_SENSOR_ENABLED
        default 4096
        help
            Stack size for the PIR monitoring task.

endmenu
